🛠️ Common DOM Methods (You’ll use these A LOT)
What You Want To Do	JavaScript Code
Grab an element by ID	    document.getElementById("myId")
Grab by class	            document.getElementsByClassName("myClass")
Grab using CSS selector	    document.querySelector(".cool")
Change text	                element.textContent = "New text!"
Change style	            element.style.color = "hotpink"
Respond to clicks	        element.addEventListener("click", () => { alert("Clicked!") })